INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (2,1,15,'<ul><li><!--block--><strong>Sanjay&nbsp;</strong><ul><li><!--block-->As last discussed, I agreed to do leadership.&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->I have to understand my new responsibility.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Forget all misshaping of past personal and professional life. Take lessons from them and try to practice it.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Yogesh devgan chahte hain ki tum ownership lo aur task khud se complete karney ka try karo. - 15-Jan-2018<ul><li><!--block-->Dusro se kaam karwao.</li><li><!--block-->Shiekh sir ne tumhhari dubara joining ke samay kaha tha ki \"<strong>Premendra management ka kaam nahi kar payega.</strong>\"<ul><li><!--block-->Tum ye baat galat saabit karo.</li><li><!--block-->Ab yaha se job se nikaal diye jaaney ki baat man se nikal do aur dusro se kaam nikalne par focus karo.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Naresh&nbsp;</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Say No to tasks for which you have no idea, like WAS configuration.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Yashwant singh</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Time se office aao, apna kaam karo aur time se nikal jao.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>and other colleagues</strong></li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>Sheikh Ibbrahim</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Dar ke rahne wala aadat chhoro.</li><li><!--block-->Sab se communicate karo.<ul><li><!--block-->19-Jan-2018<ul><li><!--block-->Sab se question karo.<ul><li><!--block-->Jab tum question karte ho toh khud hi tum dusro par haawi hone lagte ho.</li><li><!--block-->Question karney ke baad khud hi thori der me pyaar se uska answer de do. Isse dusre man hi man me ye maan lete hain ki ye banda se koi sawal nahi karna. Jo ye bol raha hai, usko maan lene me hi bhalai hai.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Try one thing- Never say \"NO\", rather first analyse issue, take understanding of problem-statement and then say \"give me 30 minutes, and thik for solution like you are going to be burnt and you will have to attempt for your last escape.\"&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Life me ek baar Sheikh sir ko bhi laga ki wo bahut sochtne lage hain.&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->Sheikh sir ke pitaji ke dehant ke baad, unke ghar ki halat sahi nahi thi. Ghar me arthik tangi thi.</li><li><!--block-->Sheikh sir sochte they ki mere sath hi aisa kyu hua.</li><li><!--block-->Fir sir ko realize hua ki \"<strong>Jo hua hai kuch acche ke liye hi hua hai</strong>\". Uske baad sheikh sir ko path mil gaya.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Team me sab se baat ko samjho, tab bahar me khud se us baat ko represent karne ka try karo. (18-Dec-2017 , take 3 months and change my behave)</li><li><!--block--><br></li></ul><div><!--block--><strong><br>Yogesh Devgan</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Don\'t chew pan masala in front of any lady employee.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Leadership</strong><ul><li><!--block-->How -&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->1) Understand the expectation-level of Management. How much I fit into it. Do I need help of others? Whom and how I will get the help?</li><li><!--block-->2) Understand and make grip on given task.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->3) Delegate the work to subordinates and monitor it.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Take understanding for CCE project.</li><li><!--block-->Humko task assign karne ke baad bhula nahi jaata. Hum chahte hain ki task assign karke hum ko follow up nahi lena pare.- 15-Jan-2018<ul><li><!--block-->Agar tumko problem hogi toh hum help karenge. but tum ownership lo aur assigned task khud se complete karne ka try karo.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Be informed from mails and tickets.</strong></li><li><!--block-->Extract RCAs for resolvejiffy and gainmanager</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>Somen Bose</strong></div><ul><li><!--block--><strong>My discussions with Somen Bose regarding my revised goals</strong><ul><li><!--block--><strong>1 st march 2018</strong><ul><li><!--block-->RJ GM - Final SME in next 3 months</li><li><!--block-->SCRM - Training Documents&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->Arrange training internal - discuss to whom training dena hai.</li><li><!--block-->Backend configuration</li><li><!--block-->Administration&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->give understanding to other team members - uni , qaa, dots</li><li><!--block-->extra movement kya le sakte hain</li><li><!--block-->kya kya activity karte ho, ek week ka -- next week ka reschedule.</li><li><!--block-->UCSR - Php -&nbsp; .net<ul><li><!--block-->KT phase 1 + Functional Understanding</li><li><!--block-->KT phase 2 + Functional Understanding</li><li><!--block-->code review&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Database analysis and review</li><li><!--block-->understanding server level configuration and management</li><li><!--block-->effective support and level-2 support</li><li><!--block-->code analysis</li><li><!--block-->Functional understanding</li><li><!--block-->Zero down time</li><li><!--block-->resolve tickets in defined TAT</li><li><!--block-->Transition</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Coordinate with team member - Team Coordination</strong><ul><li><!--block-->How -&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->2018 - Automation of support<ul><li><!--block-->How -&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Support 24*7 , extended support<ul><li><!--block-->How -&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Java Application Leadership , Also explore application of other technology<ul><li><!--block-->How -&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Collect All RFC details related to deployments in Application Support by 8 Jan and track their status.</strong></li><li><!--block-->take control of everything related to GM (Functionality, code, deployment, RFC) till 31st Dec</li><li><!--block-->Rekha will do all business related communications for GM applications.</li><li><!--block--><br></li></ul><div><!--block--><br><strong><em>Amit Tyagi</em></strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Java Leadership</li><li><!--block-->Support devops activities, if possible. Mainly for migration purposes</li></ul>','2017-10-19 23:43:14','2018-04-09 10:44:12',10,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
