INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (1,3,15,'<div><!--block-->1. People will ask \"Accenture chor ke dobara yaha kyu join kar liye?\"</div><ul><li><!--block-->Location problem and family issues</li><li><!--block-->Be calm and observe people reaction</li></ul><div><!--block-->2. People will ask \"Kam paisa me kyu join kar liye\"</div><ul><li><!--block-->Sab jagah interview se rahe they par final offer letter nahi aa raha tha. Job security nahi mil rahi thi , isiliye wapas puraney package par yahi join kar liye.</li></ul><div><!--block-->3. Management will try to put some extra pressure, with same salary package, on myself,</div><ul><li><!--block-->to manage team and work 24*7</li><li><!--block-->to go in calls and defend team for any issue occurred.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Solution</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Find ways of small excuses to get rid of extra pressure , or</li><li><!--block-->distribute the pressure to multiple persons.</li></ul></li></ul>','2017-10-20 15:34:49','2018-01-21 18:18:10',9,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (1,5,15,'<div><!--block--><strong><em>Thank you God for your blessings.</em></strong><br>- I live with my maa papa.<br>- I have my own home.<br>- I have all my organs working and I am well enough to do whatever I wish.<br>- Hum saarey pariwar se gussa ho ke Bangalore/Mumbai job karney chaley gaye the, waha bahut dukh bhoga. Family ko miss kiya. Khud ki galatiyon ka ehsas hua.&nbsp;<strong>Thank you God ki aapney wapas mujhey mere ghar bhej diya.<br>-&nbsp;</strong>Humko apne puraney company me job mil gaya. Ye mere waha par kiye huye acchey kaam aur inn logo ki acchai ke karan mila.</div>','2017-10-20 15:36:23','2017-11-15 06:45:11',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (1,6,15,'<div><!--block-->21-Oct-2017<br><br>- Today I met Aayush on the roads. He was going to take hair cut. He told me to go to home.<br>- I talked with Bipin chacha and chachi. Pahle chachi humko dekh ke muh ghuma li. phir hum chachi ko pair chu ke pranam kiye. Chacha aaj papa ki bahut shikayat kiye.Chachi boli ki woh humko pahchan nahi payi.<br>- Hum chacha ke sara baat suney.</div><ul><li><!--block-->Tuhar papa subah me uth ke koi ek aadmi ke pakad lewe lan aur gali dewe lan.</li><li><!--block-->chachi shikayat karat rahli ki maa narendra puja me aail rahe log aur bina khana khaile chal gail log.</li><li><!--block-->Papa ek baar rasta me milal rahlan aur koi baat na kailan.</li><li><!--block-->&nbsp;Phir itna bole ki aap saare bhai ek hi jaise hain. sab ko kisi na kisi chij ka ghamand hai. Appko apne friend circle ka ghamand hai.</li><li><!--block-->Hum paani pini aur chal aini.</li></ul><div><!--block-->- Shaam ko papa ke ye baat bataini, woh gussa karat rahlan ki tu daab ke baat na kar pawe le . Agar tu daab ke baat na kar paye le toh mat jaya karo.<br>- Chacha se baat kar ke aur papa ke baat sun ke lagal ki hum chacha ke ghar jaake galati kaini. Saadhu chacha humko us randi ke sath hi bandh dihan. Wo hummar well wisher naikhan.&nbsp;<br><br><br>25-Oct-2017<br><br>- Bike banwane ke liye, Abinash ke ghar ke paas gaye. Waha bike de ke wapas aa rahe they toh, Abinash se baat hui. Wo december january me apni wife ko wapas le ke aayega. Hum apna problem bataye toh, wo bhi ladki walo pe case karne ke liye kaha.<br><br></div>','2017-10-21 13:19:51','2017-10-29 06:02:12',5,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
