aa said \"<strong>agar tu apna aap ke care kar paibe, tab hi hum sab ke care kar paibe</strong>.\"</li><li><!--block--><strong>One good observation or good thing noticed/ experienced with my self.</strong><ul><li><!--block-->I tried to go bathroom without consuming Rajnigandha or gutkha or khaini.</li><li><!--block-->I drank much hot water, took aloe-vera and amla juice, drank herbal tea.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Later I experienced that my stomach got empty from its upper part.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Minute</strong><ul><li><!--block-->I felt much relief doublefold<ul><li><!--block-->I was happy for not consuming bad things.</li><li><!--block-->I felt confidence that I can resist for bad things. still I can get better results.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><br></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->-&nbsp;<strong>Issue in pipe connected with tanki of kitchen</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Papa contacted Prem ji plumber to check issue.</li><li><!--block-->He came around 11 PM. He suggested that chhat fore kar pipe badalna hoga. Papa uss samay machli laney bahar gaye they.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Rimjhim papa ko call kar ke ye baat batayi, Papa ke aanry tak \"Tau mistry\" ko chhat fodne se rok diya.</li><li><!--block-->mera estimation tha ki 3000-4000 rupiya ka kharcha hoga. Papa ne baad me 25000-30000 rupiya ka estimation bataya.</li><li><!--block-->Papa ghar pe aaye toh \"Tau mistry\" ko thora aur ceiling forne ko kaha.</li><li><!--block-->1-2 inch niche pipe sahi condition me thi, Papa ne \"Tau mistry\" ko aagey chhat forney se roka. papa ne vahi pe churi bana ke repair karney ko kaha,</li><li><!--block-->Prem mistry ne 75 rupiye ka saman mangaya. ek 4 inch pipe .75 inch wala, ek&nbsp;</li><li><!--block--><strong>minute</strong><ul><li><!--block-->total 75+150 rupiye me pipe repair ho gaya.</li><li><!--block-->Papa ney wisely tarike se total 250-300 me hi ye issue resolve kara liya.</li><li><!--block-->Agle 2 saal me ghar ke saare pipes diwar for ke thik kar