anager job re-run on UAT db server.<ul><li><!--block-->&nbsp;duplicacy removed. with help of Naveen</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->			- Resolvejiffy development call -&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->10th jan for deployment of CCTR phase 1. UAT Sign-off pending from dev team.&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->			- Resolvejiffy issue discussion post migration with Server, network and dba team.<ul><li><!--block-->&nbsp;- server team will change hyper-v, increase RAM on db server.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->-&nbsp;<strong>Discussion about Gain Manager application with Fayaz.</strong><ul><li><!--block-->GainManager is a payout calculation tool<ul><li><!--block-->It is a SOX application. It contains employee sensitive data.</li><li><!--block-->WFM and DPE mainly use this application.</li><li><!--block-->Feed-data is uploaded in GM application, based on which&nbsp;<strong>incentive&nbsp;</strong>gets calculated for agents of BPOs of different process.</li><li><!--block-->For our IT-Apps group no incentive is applicable.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>- HRIS team</strong><ul><li><!--block-->HRIS team<strong>&nbsp;looks into L1 issues of GM. Shahid knows about functionality of different parts of GM. Shahid and teams are connected with actual client. They train users for how to use the tool. They troubleshoot L1 issues of GM application.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>-Payout team</strong><ul><li><!--block--><strong>&nbsp;Mohd Asif is from \"Payout team\". He knows why to use GM application. Kis-kis jagah par GM application use ho sakta hai. He deals with actual client\'s (BPO agents\') issues.&nbsp;</strong></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block-->-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>19-Dec-2017<br><br>	-in home<br><br>		- I discussed my&nbsp;<strong>last day problem</strong>&nbsp;(I had sent mail to one person from audit team , without discussing the issue with all team members and only relying on Anshul statement that \"RJ Application\" has no \"automatic logout\" functionality, which was later found incomplete resolution given by me to audit team, as I found configuration for session-time-out in webshere as well as web.xml file for RJ application.)&nbsp;<strong>with parents.</strong><br><br>		- Papa suggested, dusre se baat karo<br><br>			- Kam shabdo me , tapak se jawab do. Galat sahi mat socho.<br><br>			- Pyaar se jawab do.<br><br>		- Maa suggested<br><br>			- Sihur shihur mat karo. Furti lao.<br><br>		- Sister said<br><br>			- Pariwar hamesha bamboo kare la hi hola.<br><br>			- Papa tuhar ka badai karas, sudhar laawe la tuhra khud mehnat kare ke padi.<br><br><br>------------------------------------------------------------<br>18-Dec-2017<br><br>	- In Office<br><br>		- One un-reported issue when users were facing intermittent page loading error in resolvejiffy. Two nodes were not running correctly.<br><br>		- In afternoon, One auditor has mailed to team. I only talked with Anshul and replied on that mail. Yogesh Devgan, Harish Bareja, Sheikh Ibbrahim- All get panicked. They helped to resolve the issue.<br><br>		- Sheikh ne pahle mere rajnigandha kam karne ki aadat ko appreciate kiya. Unhone kaha ki tune ye aadat kaise control kiya.<br><br>		- Hum Sheikh Ibbrahim se baat karne ko bechain they. Unke piche bhaag rahe they. Unhoney samjhaya ki-<br><br>			- Dar ke rahne wala aadat chhoro.<br><br>			- Sab se communicate karo.<br><br>			- Team me sab se baat ko samjho, tab bahar me khud se us baat ko represent karne ka try karo.<br>------------------------------------------<br>14-Dec-2017<br>- Papa said yesterday fufa called Narendra to say that he will return 25000 /- asap.<br>- Papa was worried that now he will not get any support from him.<br>- I talked with Anshul and discussed my issue. she said \"agar uske ghar wale uska support nahi karte toh ladki sudhri rahti\".<br>-----------------------------<br>13-Dec-2017<br>- Papa talked in morning that yestrday fua had called him and chided why he did not gave money.<br>-----------------<br><strong>12-Dec-2017<br>-&nbsp;</strong>ResolveJiffy was down in morning. BRC call started.<br><br>	<br>------------------------------------------<br><strong>11-Dec-2017<br>-&nbsp;</strong>In morning I did hot talk with papa</div><ul><li><!--block-->Relation chalane ke liye kabhi sahi hone ke baad bhi jhukna parta hai<ul><li><!--block-->Narendra supported this talk</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Final conclusion -&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->Ekta rakhni hogi</li><li><!--block-->Aage ka jyada mat socho sab accha hoga.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->- Logged one jira issue for zetta-quality module - Agent was not able to view coaching scheduled for him.</li><li><!--block-->Discussed two issues of GainManager -&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->1) AutoRevokeDaily activity mail being triggered twice&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->2) Employee tagging copy for december month - it may impact payout of january</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->some issue reported by Yogesh D. in the ResolveJiffy Dashboard for Nov 17</li><li><!--block-->HR activity pending shared by HR&nbsp;</li></ul><div><!--block-->-------------------------------<br><strong>10-Dec-2017<br></strong>- Jab koi aadmi se hum kaam karweni, tab ukra bhr pet khana khila dewe ke chahi, par ukar mazdoori me na kate ke chahi. Isse ukar kaam kare me mann lgal rahe la aur u bhi mann se thor jyada kaam kare la. (Management tactics learnt from Papa, while discussion why he gave all his labour-charge and did not bargained there.)<br><br>	- Dopahar me khane ke baad hum bahar ghumney gaye they jaha hum rajnigandha kharid kar khaye. Wapas aaney par hum jab darwaze par khade they tab hum gutkha thuk rahey they ki upar se maa dekh li hai. Maa wahi se humko ghur rahi thi. Uske adhikar se bhar kar humko dekhney aur hum par gussa karney ke karan hum baccho jaisa dar gaye hain. Maa upar chhat par bulayi hai. waha hum maa se jhuth bole hain ki hum laung kh