INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (1,19,15,'<div><!--block--><strong>14-Nov-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->I talked with Sanjay and we discussed the issue I faced in Accenture.<ul><li><!--block-->As discussed with him, he suggested that I should only take lesson from this event.<ul><li><!--block-->Usney kaha ki tumney bhi galati kiya hai.&nbsp;<strong>Tum khud ko defend nahi kiye.&nbsp;</strong>mere event se Sanjay ne bhi lesson liya ki usko bhi aagey koi offer milega toh wo alert rahega ki aisa bhi ho sakta hai.</li><li><!--block-->Mujhey HR se Jayesh ki galati batani chahiye thi ki mai apna kaam sahi se kar raha tha, but Jayesh ne meri expected help nahi&nbsp; ki.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>17-Nov-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->I talked with Nakul, Yashwant on dinner table. They asked about where do I live in Faridabad. Also they asked for my home\'s price. Nakul had point that I have purchased the home in more cost. I could get home in cheaper rate in delhi, near rohini.</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>18-Nov-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->I talked with Arvind, one of my batchmates. I discussed about my personal problem, my marital issue.</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>19-Nov-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->While walking, I met with dadaji and he asked about current status of marital issue.</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>20-Nov-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->After having lunch, I was walking with Nakul. He was suggesting that I should take some activities, like making roster, due to which I might be connected with team.</li><li><!--block-->Also he was taking that we should take care about things that after a certain age,35-40, companies would not offer jobs. We should invest some money,25000-35000, for learning new technologies to be in job.</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>27-Nov-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Anshul discussed after talking with one QAA user that 99.99% people do not accept their mistakes. In this way things go on.</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>29-Nov-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->I talked with Sanjay and discussed that I have lodged divorce petition. Also he discussed that he is planning one e-commerce website. I asked few questions to understand his definiteness of purpose.</li><li><!--block-->He pointed out that I get happy or sad very soon. This is not good. I must refrain from this.</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>05-Dec-2017</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->I asked Sanjay to go for a tea in evening. Then I wished to go on ground floor to get one Rajnigandha. I was planning to return back once I purchased the Rajnigandha. But while talking with him, he drove me to building 14 for tennins court. Actually he used to play tennis there.<ul><li><!--block-->I discussed<ul><li><!--block-->			- My personal relations with my wife. I said that she had not cooperated me for sex. She always said that she was ill in night and do not inform this to either my parents or her parents. And in morning she becomes well. Again next night she used to follow same process.</li><li><!--block-->			- Fayaz is not giving me information for common issue and functionality overview for GM. He said he would have not proper knowledge for the application. I requested him to give me some time for the discussion of GM overview from his side.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->I discussed with Somen and he gave overview of my responsibilities.<ul><li><!--block-->		He mainly focused that till 20th I should take control of everything related to GM (Functionality, code, deployment, RFC)</li><li><!--block-->		I should keep an eye on other application as well, but at last I have to lead these application.</li></ul></li></ul>','2017-11-15 06:42:26','2017-12-06 06:32:20',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (1,5,23,'<div><!--block-->- When it occurred? Who all users, locations , business processes affected due to this issue?<br>- What is initial cause of the issue? When it is reported? What initial steps were taken ?<br>- Who all persons joined the bridge?<br>- Cause Analysis</div><ul><li><!--block-->- What is initial cause?</li><li><!--block-->- What all networks, servers, DB, applications affected?</li><li><!--block-->- To find the cause break questions into what, why, which, how, who and move ahead to find the cause</li></ul><div><!--block-->- Once investigating issue and identification of solution</div><ul><li><!--block-->- Do we need downtime?</li><li><!--block-->- What all changes to be made?</li><li><!--block-->- How soon we can do the changes?<ul><li><!--block-->Who will take the downtime approval?</li><li><!--block-->What activities to be done?</li><li><!--block-->Who, teams and persons, will do the activity?</li><li><!--block-->How much time it will needed for entire activity?</li><li><!--block-->Who will give confirmation from each team?</li><li><!--block-->Which teams activities are in?</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Approvals<ul><li><!--block-->Agree from all teams about steps to perform</li><li><!--block-->Approval from business</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Excuses<ul><li><!--block-->I will be joining in just 10 minutes</li><li><!--block-->Sir is busy in some other meeting , we are trying to patch him</li><li><!--block-->Sir is on sick leave</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Eligibility to go in meeting<ul><li><!--block-->Be calm , polite</li><li><!--block-->Don\'t be in panic</li><li><!--block-->Defend self, then team<ul><li><!--block-->give resolution steps , but ask other to confirm, agree and rectify it.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Accept root cause, share resolution plan, but ask others to confirm, buy time, ask for time to implement</li></ul></li></ul>','2017-11-25 23:47:52','2017-11-25 23:57:53',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
