INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (3,1,24,'<div><!--block-->Fact :-&nbsp;<strong>Human procrastinate any issue, which they feel is not coming for any any topic or application which they are not hands on. Human want to let other go and solve that issue. They do not want to take other burden.<br><br>Scenario -&nbsp;</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Kirti,Fayaz,Anshul become alert and idle, when any issue comes. Kirti asks me that issue has been come in some QAA application , please check. That time, she was just listening one call. Most of the time, Fayaz and Kirti just go in meetings. Hopefully in this way they want to be highlighted/visible in team.</li><li><!--block-->I observed wrong here as Human do not want to be in tense situation. They know their limits, what they could do or what they dont. So they procrastinate any issue, which they feel is not coming for any any topic or application which they are not hands on.</li></ul><div><!--block--><strong><br>Common practices to avoid collision and repetition</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Redirect mail or issue to them and force them to solve the issue. If they are not willing to or not able to solve the issue then try to put own mind. I this way my leadership quality, knowledge will be highlighted.</li><li><!--block-->If I solved the issue by my own, then try to send the mail to Fayaz and Kirti so that they could do the analysis from next time.</li></ul><div><!--block--><br><strong>How you dealt</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->I resolved the issue by my own.</li></ul><div><!--block--><br></div><div><!--block--><br></div>','2017-12-06 06:22:00','2017-12-06 06:22:00',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (1,22,15,'<div><!--block--><strong><em>Gutkha khane se humko aur dusro ko kya pareshani hoti hai?<br></em></strong><br></div><ul><li><!--block-->24-Dec-2017 --&gt;&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->Self-confidence impacted hota hai. Gutkha khane se pahle ek bechaini rahti hai, fir khane ke baad pachtawa hota hai. Thori der me muh bhar jata hai. Usi samay koi baat karney aa jata hai, tab kafi inconvinience feel hota hai. Kabhi kabhi CAB me baithe rahte hain aur gutkha ke chalte muh bhara rahta hai, tab situation aisi hoti hai ki thuk bhi nahi sakte aur kuch bol bhi nahi sakte.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->06-Dec-2017<ul><li><!--block--><em>Mera daat kharab hota hai.</em></li><li><!--block--><em>Dusro ke majak ka patra bante hain. Dusre, Yogesh, Ashok ungli karte hain. Tab hi baat karte hain jab mera muh bhara hota hai.</em></li><li><!--block-->Ladkiyo ko smell se pareshani hoti hai.</li><li><!--block-->Paise faltu me kharch hote hain.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><br></li></ul>','2017-12-06 07:00:28','2017-12-24 13:42:15',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (2,22,15,'<div><!--block--><strong><em>Yeh aadat humko kaise lagi (history)?<br></em></strong><br></div><ul><li><!--block-->College time me, jab second year me Jayant ne mujhey chhor ke PriyaNaveen aur Sudhir ke sath room le liya, tab hum Bipin aur Ranjeet ke sath room le liye. Bipin gutkha aur khaini khata tha. Usko khate dekh hum bhi us se maang ke khana chalu kiye. Phir thode din me wo humko bhi kharidne ke liye bolne laga. Humko bhi internally feel hota tha ki humko usko apney upar bolney ka koi mauka nahi dena chahiye. Yeh khardney aur khilane ke bich me humko bhi interest aaney laga. Padhte samay muh me kuch rakhney ki aadat hone lagi. Vaise hi logo se dosti hone lagi jo gutkha khate they, ciggerate pite they. Acche log hum se duri banane lage.</li><li><!--block-->Shuru se hum image conscious nahi they.</li><li><!--block-->Khud par overconfidence tha ki hum iss aadat ko control kar lenge.</li><li><!--block-->Dhire dhire mere bhitar bahut sare karan se frustration badne laga. Gutkha, sharab, ciggerate, khaini se humko thora relief milta tha.<ul><li><!--block-->First year me marks kam aaya. Distinction nahi aaya.</li><li><!--block-->Jayant dusre log ke sath room le liya.</li><li><!--block-->Ghar ki sthiti sahi nahi thi.</li><li><!--block-->First year me ek ladki ko propose kar diye they. Iske chalte batchmates, senior mera majak banate they.</li><li><!--block-->Roommates mann layak nahi mile they.</li><li><!--block-->Humko feel hota tha ki hum ko log aache log ki category me nahi dekhte they.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Iss frustration se hum apney main goal se bhatakne lage they. Aur apne frustration, dukh ko dabaney ke liye, khud ko khud ki najar me hero banane ke liye, khud ko bold feel karney ke liye hum galat chijo ka sewan karney lage.</li></ul>','2017-12-06 07:18:21','2017-12-06 07:18:21',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (3,22,15,'<div><!--block--><strong><em>Kab kab humko lagta hai ki mujhey gutkha khana chor dena chaiye aur humko laga ki humko ye aadat chorney ke liye strong warning mili hai?&nbsp;<br></em></strong><br></div><ul><li><!--block--><strong>Till 23-Dec-2017 - Multiple escalation related to my habit to chew gutkha</strong><ul><li><!--block-->From morning till evening, rimjhim ne humko 2 baar papa ke gutkha ko churate pakara. ek baar hum paikhana me jakar gutkha khane gaye tab bhi rimjhim ko shak ho gaya aur usney maa se kah diya. Hum total 4 rajnigandha tulsi khaye.</li><li><!--block-->Maa machli bana rahi thi, hum se puchi ki paikhana me gutkha khaney gaye they na? hum bol diye ha.<ul><li><!--block-->Hum maa ko vishwas dilaye ki ab ye aadat chutney ke hi saare lakshan dikh rahe hai. Jindgi ke saare problems solve honey ki hi conditions dikh rahi hai.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Multiple escalation related to my habit to chew gutkha</strong><ul><li><!--block-->From morning till evening, rimjhim ne humko 2 baar papa ke gutkha ko churate pakara. ek baar hum paikhana me jakar gutkha khane gaye tab bhi rimjhim ko shak ho gaya aur usney maa se kah diya. Hum total 4 rajnigandha tulsi khaye.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->10-Dec-2017 - Dopahar me khane ke baad hum bahar ghumney gaye they jaha hum rajnigandha kharid kar khaye. Wapas aaney par hum jab darwaze par khade they tab hum gutkha thuk rahey they ki upar se maa dekh li hai. Maa wahi se humko ghur rahi thi. Uske adhikar se bhar kar humko dekhney aur hum par gussa karney ke karan hum baccho jaisa dar gaye hain. Maa upar chhat par bulayi hai. waha hum maa se jhuth bole hain ki hum laung kha kar thuk rahe they.&nbsp; Maa humse boli ki tu kutta hai tu sudhar nahi sakta. Hum maa se boley ki maa kutta na sudhr saka ta par kutta ke pilla sudhar saka ta.&nbsp;<strong>Hum maa se wada kiye ki hum ab gutkha na khayem.&nbsp;</strong></li><li><!--block-->Yogesh devgan ne November me mere pocket se gire Vimal ke packet ko mujhey vapas kiya. Tab bahut strong shame feel kiye they mann me. Mann kiya ki hum usi samay yeh aadat chor de.</li><li><!--block-->Humko gutkha, sharab , ciggerate , khaini ke sewan ke baad humesha laga hai ki hum galat kar rahe hain.</li><li><!--block-->Jab dusre mera majak banate hain, usi samay log mere se baat karna chahte hain, tab iss aadat ke liye afsos hota&nbsp; hai.</li></ul>','2017-12-06 07:23:45','2017-12-24 11:00:19',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (4,22,15,'<div><!--block--><strong><em>Kaun si chijein humko gutkha khaney ko vivash karti hai?</em></strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Mere mann ka frustration.</li><li><!--block-->Mera current situation me \"at a loss\" position me chale jana.<ul><li><!--block-->Jab ek sath multiple kaam dikhte hain.</li><li><!--block-->Jab papa humko datate hain.</li><li><!--block-->Jab gurgaon janey ke liye cab jaldi nahi milti hai.</li><li><!--block-->Jab apne past life ki galatiyon ko dekhte hain.</li></ul></li></ul>','2017-12-06 07:27:07','2017-12-06 07:27:07',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
