ey khud se kuch aisa mail kiya ki mera kaam highlight hota rahe.</li><li><!--block-->Shaam ko apna laptop building#14 me jama kara diye.</li><li><!--block-->Office me 200 ka rg aur cig consume kiye.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Raat me 9:30 tak ghar aa gaye. Khana khaye aur so gaye.</li></ul><div><!--block-->-------------------------------------------------------<br>14-Jan-2018 to 18-Jan-2018 ---&nbsp;<strong>Divya gyan</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Home<ul><li><!--block-->Papa maa rimi narendra se man bhar baat hua<ul><li><!--block-->Minute<ul><li><!--block-->Sab me kami hota hai. Kami chhor ke apne matlab ke chij par focus karo , apne duties ka palan karo, khush raho.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Burai ko apne man se nikalo.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block-->----------------------------------------------------------------<br>13-Jan-2017</div><ul><li><!--block-->- I woke up around 5:30 AM.</li><li><!--block-->Took medicine, tea</li><li><!--block-->Requested didi to give her rope , i tried to do rope jumping exercise. Rassi tut gaya.</li><li><!--block-->Papa ke tokney par, Hum 6:15 me tahalney chale gaye.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Tahalney aur gutkha ke dukan khojney ke dauran hum mandir pahuch gaye. vaha aarti me shamil huye.<ul><li><!--block-->Arti ke baad pandit ji prasad diye. Hum unko bole ke thonga me prasad dijiye. Vo apne ek chela se 500 rupiye ka thonga laney ko kahey.</li><li><!--block-->Humse pandit ji bole \"Sector me hi ek family hai, ladka aur pariwar ke bare me bologe toh detail de denge\".&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->Hum koi reaction nahi diye. Kyuki hum toh koi aur tension (apne&nbsp;<strong>kisi biti baat par overthinking ki problem ke solution find karney</strong>&nbsp;ko mind me le ke mandir pahuchey they)<ul><li><!--block-->Humko aisa laga ki mandir me bhagwan ka aadesh hai ki \"<strong>jab kisi biti ghatna ke upar man ghabraye ta bas ye kaho ki hanuman ji hum falanwa kaam galat ya sahi kar diye hain, khata me likh likh lijiyega aur kuch rebate ho to voh bhi kar dijiyega</strong>\"</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Ghar par aake jaldi se naha liye. Nahaney se pahle gutkha khaye aur paikhana me gaye. but waha late honey ke khayal se gutkha thuk ke nahae chale gaye.</li><li><!--block-->Nashta kar ke office ke liye nikle, raste me kirti ko call kar ke bol diya ki wo 8:30 ke baad GM activity start kar de, agar hum late ho toh.</li><li><!--block-->Fir Yogesh devgan ko message kar diya ki raste me hain.</li><li><!--block-->Office 8:45 AM me pahuch gaye,&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->GM Payout activity ke steps note karney lage ek word document me.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Kirti se baat kiye</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Kirti lucknow ki hai. 2 bahen aur ek bhai. Kirti mid me hai.</li><li><!--block-->Kirti ko apni life se judi kuch baate bataye,&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->jaise meri shaadi,&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->ladki ka mere sath nahi rahna, jhagra karna.</li><li><!--block-->Mere aur pariwar ke according behave nahi karna</li><li><!--block-->Unki family ka hum logo se kabhi contact nahi karna.</li><li><!--block-->Hum logo ka ladka wala honey ke bawjood unke pass jana aur ladki ko december me le ke aana.</li><li><!--block-->Fir ladki ka apne chote bhai ke sath chale jana.</li><li><!--block-->Unke aur hamare side se legal actions ka status, abhi november me hum divorce case file kar diye hain.</li><li><!--block-->Isi sab ke chalte hum sab ladki ko bahan ki nazar se toh dekh sakte hai, but dubara shaadi karney me mera koi interest nahi hai.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Kirti ne apne baare me bataya ki<ul><li><!--block-->Jo log mera trust todte hain wo mujhey pasand nahi.</li><li><!--block-->personal life ke baare me ek hudd ke baad sab koi ko nahi batana chahiye.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Agar koi mera trust todta hai toh mai chupp ho jati hu. Uski kisi baat ka jawab nahi deti.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Kirti has worked on several new tools like CXP,&nbsp;</li><li><!--block--><strong>Learnings - Jyada mat socho. Jab ek topic ya chij se mann bhar jaye toh, kuch change try karo.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Satish Verma 2:30 me office aaya. Satish se baat kiye.</strong><ul><li><!--block-->As discussed, he blames others to not sharing full information.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->I suggested to have willingness to observe things.</li><li><!--block-->He is from jharkhand, but he is not much trustworthy. He is careless.</li><li><!--block-->Satish Verma is also doing Freelancing projects and also maintains some contacts for front end developers.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Learnings - Jitni salary mil rahi hai, usi ke according kaam karna chahiye. Apna mast life jina chahiye.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Raat me 9:30 PM par Yogesh Devgan ko \"Gain Manager Payout activity\" ka final status de ke ghar ke liye nikal gaye.</li><li><!--block-->Ghar pe maa se baat kiye.<ul><li><!--block-->Maa ko bataye ki aaj&nbsp; ek ladki ke sath office me they. Pahli baar kisi ladki se baat kiye.&nbsp;<strong>Agar ladki ko faith ho ki ye ladka acchi niyat se mere se baat karta hai, tabhi wo baat karti hai.</strong></li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block--><br>--------------------------------------<br>12-Jan-2018</div><ul><li><!--block-->Home&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->- Subah me Maa se baat hui. Maa bata rahi thi ki papa baar-baar puja path ka waste, calender aur other kaagaz, jala dete hain. Maa ro rahi thi.</li><li><!--block-->&nbsp; - Maa ko samjhaye ki tu unko samjha di aur wo nahi maane, ab unko bolna chor de. saaman idhar udhar rakhne ki jagah Vahi rakho.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->	-&nbsp;<strong>Man shant rakho, jo hona hoga vahi hoga. Bhagwan kabhi apne par dosh nahi lete. Hum jo karte hain usi ka fal samney aata hai. dimag se ye baat nikal do ki kuch bura hoga.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Office<ul><li><!--block-->In office day was good, 2&nbsp; ResolveJiffy issue came, but no issue found from our side.