ock-->1.30-2.30 hrs - avg 2 hrs commute back to home</li><li><!--block-->1 hrs dress for night + dinner</li><li><!--block-->1-2 hrs prepare for next day + analysis of day</li><li><!--block-->5-8 hrs sleep</li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block-->-&nbsp;<strong>In office,</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Took update from Kirti for<ul><li><!--block-->RJ CCTR Deployment approval process is in progress.</li><li><!--block-->UAT Sign-off not reecieved</li><li><!--block-->GM job has been run successfully this month.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Shared same to Yogesh.</li><li><!--block-->Tried to investigate one Zetta coaching issue&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->One person from same sector met from Sikandarpur.<ul><li><!--block-->He can pick and drop me to office every day. charge 50/-.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>What escalation&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><div><!--block-->------------------------------<br>01-Jan-2018</div><ul><li><!--block-->Happy New Year</li><li><!--block-->Office<ul><li><!--block-->Aaj Yogesh sir se baat hui<ul><li><!--block-->Unko call kiye new year ke liye</li><li><!--block-->Allegation - no preventive action taken for gainmanager monthly job</li><li><!--block-->My allegation - no proper information being provided</li><li><!--block-->Will discuss on Wednesday</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Home<ul><li><!--block-->I discussed same with maa and narendra. They said \"<strong>hamesha socho kuch nahi hoga</strong>\".. Koi na koi rasta niklega</li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block-->--------------------------------<br>11-Dec-2018</div><ul><li><!--block-->Sab accha hoga.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Hum sharafat ka chola odhna chate hain. Chahte hain ki dusre mere liye defend kare.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Hum bure hain. Dusre mere baare me bura sochte hain, par accha bolte hain. Humko bhi accha bolna hai.</strong></li></ul><div><!--block-->-------------------------------------<br><strong>05-Dec-2017 to 10-Dec-2017<br></strong><br></div><ul><li><!--bloc