INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (6,2,15,'<div><!--block--><strong>Shri Mata Vaishno devi darbar</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Vighn aate hain, aapko un ko pahchan ke aur un se bach ke apne karm ko karna hota hai.</li><li><!--block-->Dharm pariksha leta hai. Aniti ko pahchan ke apne karm ko karna chahiye.</li><li><!--block-->Swarg pahuchney ke do raste hain. Koi sukh bhog ke swarg jata hai aur koi dukh bhog ke. Apne karm ko pahchan ke bas us path par badhte rahna chahiye.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Manushya ke jiwan me kasht aate hain. Kashto ka samna karna chaiye. Kashto ka samna karne se manushya ka jiwan mahan hota hai. Aasakti aur Laparwahi se vighna aur pareshaniya hoti hai. Aaskti aur Laparwahi nahi karni chahiye.</strong></li><li><!--block-->Iss sansar me sab koi apne liye hi jita hai.<ul><li><!--block-->Ek ladka ek sanyasi ke pass gaya aur usey bolne laga ki aap sirf sansarik batein hi toh pravachan me batate hain. Tab sanyasi ne usko kaha ki ye dawa pilo aur tumhare saare ang shithil ho jayenge. Us ladke ne dawa pili. Tab sanyasi ne uske pariwar ke sab dusre sadasyo ko bula ke kaha ki tum me se koi ek ye dudri dawa pilo aur ye ladka thik ho jayega. But wo vyakti mar jayega. Sab ney koi na koi bahana banaya par wo dawa nahi pi. Tab ladke ko gyan prapt hua ki \"<strong>Iss duniya me sab apney liye hi jite hain, sare rishte naate maaya hai aur vyakti sansarik moh maya me fas kar dukh hi pata hai.</strong>\"</li><li><!--block--><strong>Live example from my life-&nbsp;</strong><ul><li><!--block-->19-Feb-2018 - I had doubt on above teachings. Hum 8:00 baje gym ke liye nikle. Par gym ke pass pahuch kar sadhu chacha ke ghar chale gaye. Chachi aur Chacha ne ajnabi ke jaisa vyavhar kiya. Chacha bol rahe they ki jab tak tuhar&nbsp;<strong>papa katu vachan bolal aur gali dewal na chorihan, rishta naata na ban payi.&nbsp;</strong>Chacha chachi mere case ke liye puch rahe they. Chachi boli ki tuhar vajan kam bhel ba, hum chacha ko hus deni ki wo appan umar ke log se bhi budha lage lan. Chacha sun lelan, puchlan ta hum bol deni ki ha chacha tuhar shikayat karat rahni chachi se.Last me chachi humko chai ke liye roki. humko laga ki dusra cup chai chacha piyenge, but wo toh sunil ke liye tha. Humko bahut kaharab laga, aur hum chai adhura chor kar chacha chachi ko pranam kar ke vapas aa gaye.&nbsp;<strong>Humko samajh jana chachiye ki ab mere liye koi rishta naata nahi hai. Apne baare me socho premendra !!!!!!!!!!!!!!</strong></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Vyakti ko madhur vachan bolney chahiye. Wo bolna chahiye jo dusro ko acha lage.</li><li><!--block-->Siddhi kya hai. Koi bhi maa bhagwati/Mahadev ji ka mantra jo baar baar chintan manan kiya gaya ho, vahi ek samay ke baad Siddhi ho jati hai.</li></ul>','2018-01-20 01:37:53','2018-02-19 09:03:47',10,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (7,2,15,'<div><!--block--><strong>Self</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->08-July-2017<ul><li><!--block-->Hum khud se bahut baat karte hain, Humko ghamand bahut jaldi ho jata hai.</li><li><!--block-->Ghamand ka ulta namrata hota hai.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->05-July-2017<ul><li><!--block--><strong>Meri help agar koi karega toh woh mai hi hu.</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Ek baar issue analyse kar lenge toh fir 60 % issue hum khud hi solve kar sakte hain. Baaki 40% issue ke liye well wishers ko call kar sakte hain.</li><li><!--block-->Iss gyan ki keemat mera Accenture ka job hai.<ul><li><!--block-->Yaha mai dusro se help mangta raha, proper response nahi kiya ki ye kaam me mujhey jyada time lag sakta hai. Chup raha aur usko manager ne ego pe le liya. Aur mera job janey wala hai.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>','2018-01-20 02:11:31','2018-01-20 02:11:31',1,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (4,24,15,'<div><!--block-->2017 - During leaving from accenture</div><ul><li><!--block--><strong><em>31-Dec-2017 --&nbsp;</em></strong><strong>Confession with self.</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Mere mann me ek shaitan baitha hua lagta hai jo baar baar humko galat hi suggestion deta hai.<ul><li><!--block-->Ki gutkha khao.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Hum solutions ke liye nahi soch paate<ul><li><!--block--><strong>Duniya me sabko unke problems/queries ka solution hi chahiye.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Hum khud ko dhokha dete hai.</li><li><!--block-->Problems ko bada kar ke sochte hain.<ul><li><!--block-->Jabki , sirf itna sochney se kaam chal sakta hai ki&nbsp;<strong>Humko shant rahna hai, dusro ko observer karna hai ki wo kis type ka reaction dete hain</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Mera problem hai ki<ul><li><!--block-->Hum response nahi karte<ul><li><!--block-->Aur agar karte bhi hai toh galat jagah, galat tareeke se, ya jyada bol dete hain.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Gutkha khane, ciggerate pine ke chalte social nahi ho paate.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Khud par vishwas nahi hai.<ul><li><!--block-->Dusro ko khud se accha samajh lete hain&nbsp;<ul><li><!--block-->aur explain karne lagte hain ki hum bhi acche hain.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->22-July-2017<ul><li><!--block-->Aaj Capgemini ka interview diya.<ul><li><!--block-->Can we create collections of interface objects?</li><li><!--block-->How to prevent web applications from different malware attacks.<ul><li><!--block-->Like multiple requests coming to the applications to choke it.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->18-July-2017<ul><li><!--block-->Mere Accenture me failure ka following cause hai.<ul><li><!--block-->4 saal support profile me kaam kiya par hamesha mera mann development profile me jaane ka karta tha. Maine internet se download karke interview questions yaad kiye. Par practice nahi ki. Yaha expectations poora nahi kar paaye aur performance me fas gaye.</li><li><!--block-->Apni profile aur niji jindgi ke problem se yaha kisi se dosti nahi kar paaye. Proper response nahi diya aur sab mere against ho gaye. Managers jab mera defend kar rahe they tab DU Lead ke paas bakwas kar aaye ki mujhey kuch nahi aata, hum ko jaaney do, humko nikal do.</li><li><!--block-->Khud ko defend karney ki jagah, khud ko weaker bana ke exposed kar diya.</li><li><!--block-->Khud ki burai par control nahi kiya, isiliye fail ho gaya.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->10-July-2017<ul><li><!--block-->Last week<ul><li><!--block-->infosys me interview dene gaye they.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Marine drive ghumey gaye</li><li><!--block-->Sunday ko office gaye</li><li><!--block-->Shaam ko D-mart se shopping kiye</li><li><!--block-->Ghar pe baat kiye.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Aaj gym me ek dost banaye.<ul><li><!--block-->Isse jiwan ki chinta kam lag rahi hai.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->08-July-2017<ul><li><!--block-->Aaj Infosys ka interview dene gaye they.<ul><li><!--block-->Aap kis chij me expert hain.</li><li><!--block-->Aap itni jaldi job kyu change karna chate hain.</li><li><!--block-->Estimation ka kon kon sa tool hota hai.</li><li><!--block-->Appney kon kon se tool par kaam kiya hai.</li><li><!--block-->Aap future me kya banna chahte hain<ul><li><!--block-->Agar aap Software Architect banna chahte hain toh kya aapko pata hai ki software architect kya karta hai.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Team handling kya hota hai.<ul><li><!--block-->Team handling me kya karna hota hai</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>','2018-01-20 02:28:25','2018-01-20 02:59:13',9,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
