INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (11,24,15,'<div><!--block--><strong>10-Oct-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->NALCO, UPRVUNL, CSPHCL</li><li><!--block-->Atmavishwas acchey kaam karney se aata hai. Atmavishwas apney mann ki aawaz hai. Atmavishwas hausla deta hai, jujhney ki</li><li><!--block--><strong>This is my motto</strong><ul><li><!--block-->GAP rokna hai</li><li><!--block-->Experience lena hai.</li><li><!--block-->Jam ke taiyari karna hai.</li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>09-Oct-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Aaj ek baar mai us \"<strong>Premendra</strong>\" ki yaad karna chahta hu, jo mai ban sakta tha aur aaj bhi mann ke kisi koney me dubka pada hai.<ul><li><!--block-->Vah \"<strong>Premendra</strong>\", jo ciggerate gutkha aadi buraiyon se door rahta hai.</li><li><!--block-->Vah \"<strong>Premendra</strong>\" jo ishwar ko manta hai aur manta hai ki apna kaam imaandari se karney walo ko hi ishwar sahayta karta hai.</li><li><!--block-->Vah \"<strong>Premendra</strong>\" jo nirasha me bhi aasha ki kiran ko hi dekhta hai aur jiska ek hi siddhant hai ki \"<strong><em>Chahe mai ghistunga, rengunga, par mai sirf apney lakshya ki taraf hi badhunga aur mere lakshya ki taraf badha ek kadam mujhey lakshya se ek kadam najdeek kar dega</em></strong>\"</li><li><!--block-->Vah \"<strong>Premendra</strong>\" jo dusro ka dil nahi dukhata aur bevajah naraz honey walo se khud hi naraz ho jata hai.</li><li><!--block-->Vah \"<strong>Premendra</strong>\" jo jiwan me hamesha aasha ki kiran dekhta hai aur nirantar apney lakshya ki taraf badhney ko agrasar hai. ---&nbsp;<strong><em>Premendra 09/Oct/2010</em></strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>JANAMI DHARMAM NA CHA ME PRAVRITIH |, JANAMYAADHARMAM NA CHA ME NIVRITIH ||</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Anjaaney ME KOI APRADH HO TOH WO KSHAMYA HO SAKTA HAI, PAR JAANBUJH KE KIYA GAYA APRADH AKSHAMYA HO JATA HAI. Mainey jaan-bujh ke apradh kiye hain. Isiliye mujhey jail-jaisi saza huyi hai. Aaj yaha par mere paas pita ka paisa hai. Khana kha chuka hu. Sangeet sun raha hu.&nbsp;<strong>Par akela hu. Koi nahi jisse batiya saku.&nbsp;</strong>Padhai me man nahi lag pa raha hai.&nbsp;<strong><em>Abhi iss samay sabse jyada jarurat mehnat, lagan aur parishram se apni padhayi karney ki hai aur mai iss kaam me khud ko saksham nahi pa raha hu.&nbsp;</em></strong>Koi chij acchi nahi lag rahi hai. -&nbsp;<strong><em>Premendra 09/Oct/2010</em></strong></li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>02-Sep-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Mai manta hu ki mujhse galatiyaan ho jaati hain aur kuch galatiyaan mai kar chuka hu - kuch jaan bujh kar aur kuch anjaaney me - par ab sochna ye hai ki aage kya karna hai, ki gayi galatiyon ko rona hai ya jo sapna man me dekha hai usey poora karna -&nbsp;<strong><em>Premendra, 02/09/2010</em></strong></li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>28-Aug-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block--><strong>Kami kaha hai?</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Ghar se soney, pahanney,udaney ke liye paisa mil raha hai.</li><li><!--block-->Yaha rahney, soney aur padhney ka mahoul hai.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Kami sirf hum me hai. Nahi kar pa rahe hain. Karan man ki bechaini, ya aur kuch bhi ho, hum nahi kar pa rahe hain.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>My confession</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Duniya gol hai. Vaqt ke sath duniya aage badhti hai, par ek din phir usi jagah pahuch jati hai, jaha safar shuru huya tha. Aaj jo dikhta hai, vahi kal bhi tha aur vahi parso bhi hoga. Badlega toh wo honge iss duniya ko dekhney, sunne aur samajhney wale.<ul><li><!--block-->Ye bhumika hai uss baat ki jisey aaj mere mann ne bahut gahrai se mahsus kiya aur sacchai ko anuman lagakar mann darr gaya.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Jiwan me aur iss duniya me,&nbsp; uss vishal parwat aur ussey bahati kal-kal karti Ganga-sa sambandh hai. Duniya vah vishal parwat hai, jaha ek unchey gomukh se jiwan-rupi Ganga nikalti hai aur parwat se apni hi chal me nikalti chali jaati hai. Jiwan ki ek disha hai aur uss disha me ye badhti jaati hai. Jindgi ka ek bhi bita pal, Ganga ki uss dhara ki tarah hai, jo parwat se utartkar maidan me aa gayi hai aur ab wo parwat par vapas nahi ja sakti.</strong></li><li><!--block-->Jiwan badhta hi chala jata hai . Aur hum jeev, jo jiwan ko apni aatma me dharan karte hain, samajhte hain ki duniya chal rahi hai. Jabki chalna jeewan ko hi hai, duniya vahi thi, hai aur rahegi.</li><li><!--block-->Ye baatein mere mann me aayi, toh isiliye nahi ki mujhey likhna accha lagta ho, ya mujhey kuch samajh aa gaya hai.&nbsp;<strong>Balki isiliye ki ab mai samajh gaya hu ki ab mere jiwan me badlaw aaney wale hain. Sadharan shabdo me, mainey mahsoos kiya ki aaj mere vartmaan pariprekshya me aagey kya ho sakta hai aur wo kitna bhayawah hoga.</strong></li><li><!--block-->Aaj mai ek vidhyarthi hu. Sahi-galat karte huye jiwan me kuch sikh raha hu. Par meri chal wo nahi, jo honi chahiye. Parwat se girta Ganga ka paani yahi samajhta hai ki ye meri mastani chal aur mera kal-kal jhal-jhal girta roop hamesha hi rahega aur iss bhram me wo kabhi-kabhi kisi vishal parwat ghaati me vishram kar leti hai. Par ye hi bhool hai, jo maidani bhaag ke samney aaney par hi dhristigochar ho paati hai.<ul><li><!--block-->Thik aise hi jindgi ko mainey aaj tak kharch kiya. Jiwan ki shruaat honey aur meri chetna ke jagney ke liye jis samay-antral me mera lakshya aagey badhna hona chahiye tha, wo lakshya aaj tak prapt ho jana tha.&nbsp;<strong>Par Ganga ki unn jal-tarango ki tarah mai ek awrodh par vishram karney laga.&nbsp;</strong>Jis awrodh ko mujhey khil-khil kar ke aagey jana tha, wahin mainey vishram ka man bana liya.&nbsp; Maidani bhag me aaney par, jaise Ganga ki jal-tarangein jaise dhimi par jaati hain, thik vaisey hi ab jiwan ke unchey-nichey raste ab sapat aur tedhe hote ja rahe hain.</li><li><!--block-->Par ye toh hona hi tha, jab jal-tarangein maidan me aayin.&nbsp;<strong>Par kuch toh hua, jo hona na tha. Ye tha uss bandh par vishram karna.&nbsp;</strong>Par ab kya ho? Jiwan ab ek shant, veeran aur akele safar par chal padi hai.&nbsp;<strong>Ab raste aur tedhey-medhey aur chaal aur dhimi hi honi hai.</strong></li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Agar mera yah model, jiwan ko kuch hadd tak samjhata hai, to wo bhawishya ki bhi ek dhundhli tasweer ki rachna kar sakta hai. Uss tasweer me, jaha khel wahi hai, par sirf mohre badal rahe hain aur usi ke anusar khiladiyon ka ohda aur unki sanrachna, sochney samajhney ka awsar milta hai.</li><li><!--block-->Agar aaj mainey galati ki, aur kisi aur ne wo galati 10-15 saal pahle ki ho, to agar mainey ye galati chaalu rakhi , toh mera bhi wahi hashra hoga, jo uss \"Kisis aur\" ka aaj hai; ya sthiti isi ke ird-gird hi hogi.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Aur agar avrodhon ki vimayen, toh unka jiwan par asar bahu-vimiy hoga. -&nbsp;</strong>Yahi hai wo darr jo mann me aata hai. -&nbsp;<strong><em>Premendra 25/Aug/2010</em></strong>&nbsp;</li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block--><br><strong>19-Aug-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Kuch samajh nahi aata ki aage kya karu? dekhte-dekhte ye samay nikal gaya aur aaj ye nahi tay kar pa raha ki kya khoya aur kya paya? inn beete huye 1 saal me. Ummid ki kiran dikhti hai aur phir gayab ho jaati hai. Aage jindgi kaun si karwat legi, tay nahi kar pa raha.</li><li><!--block-->Sochta hu ki apni naukri kar lunga, uske pahle jam ke taiyari kar lunga. Par kar nahi pa raha. Mann me tarah tarah ke vichar aate hain aur mai unn vicharon me apni manjil bhul jata hu. Raat ko nind nahi aati aur dinn ko chain nahi rahta. Mann ko ekagra nahi kar pata.</li><li><!--block-->Janta hu ki meri samasya ka hal bhi mere hi pass hai. Mann laga ke taiyari karni hai aur parinaam sukhad hoga. Par mann nahi laga pa raha. Khud ki hi galati hai. Par sudharney ka rasta nahi sujh raha.</li><li><!--block-->Mera antarman kahta hai ki mai wo sab kar sakta hu, jo mai chahta hu. Jaise ki khub acchey se padhai kar sakta hu aur apney aap ko khush rakhte huye apney sharir par dhyan de sakta hu.Ya phirr apney bhitar ki sabhi buraiyon ko ek jhatke me door kar sakta hu.<ul><li><!--block-->\"<strong>Parr .. aur sari musibatein isi parr.. kintu .. parantu.. ityaadi\"&nbsp;</strong>se ho jaati hai. Mann me aayi antarman ki aawaz kahi dab jaati hai aur mai khud ko bechain, akela, lachar, mazboor aur samasyaon tatha nirasha se ghira mahsus karney lagta hu. Ek pal me hi wo sara junoon, utsah aur josh samapt ho jata hai. Aakho ke aagey ek andhera chha jata hai aur mann tarah tarah ki bhawna-sambhawna aur hone-nahi-hone ke chakkar me fas jata hai.</li></ul></li><li><!--block-->Ho sakta hai, arthaat mai puri tarah se janta toh nahi par mahsoos hota hai, ki mere mann me aaney wali bhawnaon ka koi matlab nahi ho, par phir bhi dil ghabra jata hai. Jaise paani me doobta koi kisi sahare ki talash me hath-paav marta hai aur lahron se ladney ki jagah doobta jata hai, kuch vaisa hi mere sath har roz hota hai. Aur mai bas ek mook-darshak-jaisa kim-kartawya-vimood hoke sirf sochta rah jaata hu.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Kya karu? bas isi prashna me uljha rahta hu. Kya mai jo soch raha hu wo sahi hai? - ye sawal barabar dimag ko asthir banaye rakhta hai.&nbsp;</strong>Kaise naiya paar hogi?- bas ye baat man ko bechain kiye deti hai. -&nbsp;<strong><em>Premendra 19/Aug/2010</em></strong></li></ul><div><!--block--><br><strong>13-Aug-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block--><strong>What if my God asks me to which kind of companion do you want and promises to fulfill exactly the same,&nbsp; what should my answer?</strong><ul><li><!--block-->I have very beautiful imagination of my life-partner. Everyone wants beautiful lady as his co-partner. That is the one of the most necessity of most of the people in this world.&nbsp; But something is also in this world is need afterall. I want also a good, cute, charming and a dazzling beauty. And after finding such an unique partner I\'ll wish and pray to God. But if I may have to compromise with the beauty of my lifepartner, as mostly people have to do ( afterall no one can get the good one because then what for the rest!), then I want she should always be cheerful, cooperative and with good sense of humor.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->But if it is also a different task for God to allot me such a life-partner with optimum beauty, with cheerful, cooperative and good sense of humor, I want such a girl as my life-partner who can understand me and pusuade me time to time and obviously the time I need it really.</li><li><!--block-->I don\'t know how exactly she will but I have a very enthusiasm about her. How other people get a companion of their favor, I want to get my dreams imagination&nbsp; to come over the earth.</li><li><!--block-->When I\'ll meet her first time, what if my reaction? I don\'t know but she is some other than my imagination.</li><li><!--block-->How she will smile with me and I will see only in her eyes. I also want to request to God give me such a good friend like co-partner, that she must have big eyes like a beautiful female-deer. Her eyes must have an attraction that I loose all my tension and start to talk with her hours and hours. I just see in her eyes and say all the things which effervesce in my heart and she reacts in such a way that I just move ahead and step more.</li><li><!--block-->A big room, with well furnished furniture. A big bed on which there is a well-mannered dunlop and a big light-rose-colored bed-sheet. A deem-light and a song from my choice in very slow volume. The air is just after a rain and it has so freshness and good smell that rejuvenate we both. She smiles and move towards me and I towards her while talking. I, as more I say as she moves towards me and confidently watch in my eyes and I see the confidence and love in her eyes. She sometimes smiles during the conversation without watching on either the clocks or anything else. I just want to go deep inside her eyes. She sometimes raise her hands to rearrange the hairs which have come on the front face but I stop her hands by my hands because I feel an interrupt and I by my ownself start to rearrange those hairs in my own way. I just take the front hairs and take them just back of the ears and slowly touch her face and say her with an artificial anger to try to concentrate dear. And then I, with an an artificial expression, say that where I was and then she explains everything in the same fashion in what manner I told to her. This makes me happy and become delighted in my own inner-heart. Then I take the conversation afterward.</li><li><!--block-->That beautiful night, with her, in a big well furnished room, on a big bed with big dunlop and over which a light-rose-colored bedsheet, over which I explain every my feelings that currently efferves in my mind and she curiously listen everything. The very dramatic and romantic situation. The light music in my room is so fantastically making the environment light and I just enjoying these all with my spouse. In the moon-light, which is coming from windows on which a silky curtain is just flowing with wind, which is coming from the half closed windows glass and making us both more and more romantic.</li></ul></li></ul><div><!--block--><br><br><strong>28-Jan-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->Kya likhu , mai khud se nirash ho gaya hu. Samajh nahi pa raha hu kya sahi hai. Dil me ek bojh sa ho gaya hai. Bahut dino se safalta nahi mil payi hai. Ya yu kahu ki bahut dino se thik se mehnat nahi kar pa raha hu. Mai khud se hi naraz hu. Mai khud ko jis mukam par dekhna chahta hu, usi ke liye taiyar nahi kar pa raha hu. Ek baar meri gaadi rukti hai toh phir khud ko usi jagah pata hu jaha se chala tha.&nbsp;</li><li><!--block-->Udhar maa-papa aas lagaye baithey hain ki kab mai kuch karunga. Kab unhey kahunga ki mai apney pairo par khada ho gaya. Sabhi gharwale aas lagaye hain ki mai padhkar ek mukam haasil karu. Aur yaha mai khud se jujh raha hu. Apney bhitar soye huye josh ko talash raha hu. Kuch dino ke liye josh aata hai. Par phir na jane kaise mai phir se usi soch me doob jata hu ki kaise aage badhunga mai, jabki mai puri tarah taiyar nahi hu. Khud se jujhta hu aur dil hi dil me rota hu. Phir duniya ki ranginiyo me doobkar apni kamiyo ko bhul jana chahta hu. Shayad kismat bhi sath nahi de rahi, isiliye mujhey recession ka ek bahana bhi mil gaya hai apni kamiyo par chadar karney ke liye.</li><li><!--block-->Sabhi sacchai samajh rahe hain. Par mai toh jantya hi hu ki mai apni duty thik se nahi kar pa raha hu. Jaaney kab tak chalega ye? Mai ghar par toh jhuth bol deta hu ki ha padhai ho rahi hai, par kya apno ko mai chhal pa raha hu? Lagta hai ki majil thori hi door hai. Par chalney ki himmat nahi karta hu. Safalta ka sapna toh dekh raha hu, par mehnat se katrata hu.</li><li><!--block-->Khyalo me toh kai saare sapney dekha leta hu par vashtavikta me kuch nahi kar raha hu. Bas jindgi ko bojh ki tarah dho raha hu.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Meri bas khud se ek hji shikayat hai ki agar khub mehnat ki hoti toh shayad kahi aur khub acchey se hota. Par khud me ikshashakti ki kami mahsoos hoti hai.</strong></li><li><!--block--><strong>Roz subah uthkar khud pe rota hu. Phir ulte-sidhey tareeke se khud ko manakar mehnat karney se khud ko bacha leta hu. Par aakhir kab tak? Akhir kis se jhuth bolta hu. Kisko dhokha deta hu? Mai sirf sansadhano ka durupayog kar raha hu.</strong></li><li><!--block--><strong>Sacche dil se kahu toh kami khud me hi dikhti hai. Apni saari pareshaniyo ka karan khud me hi pata hu. Ek baar mehnat karna shuru kar du toh shayad manjil jyada door nahi hai. Par khud ko kaise samjhau?&nbsp;</strong>Shayad koi dusra hota toh use samjhata, usey fatkarta, usey sahi rah dikhata aur apna ji-jaan laga deta ki sahi rasta usey dikh jaaye, par khud par jor nahi chalta.</li><li><!--block-->Mainey apni samasya kabhi apney maa-papa ya anya kisi ko nahi batayi. Khud me hi ghutata rahta hu. Sochta hu ki unhey dukha hoga, ye jaan kar ki mai aajtak unhey dhokha deta raha. Par sacchey dil se, dil par hath rakha kar sochta hu ki kya mai sahi kar raha hu? Kya sahi me unhey sacchai nahi pata chal rahi hogi ki mai kya kar raha hu?</li><li><!--block--><strong>Shayad Ishwar mere sath hai. Isiliye wo sabhi ko chhup rakhey huye hai. Unhey dhiraj bandhaye huye hai ki ek din mai safal jarur howunga.&nbsp;</strong></li><li><!--block--><strong>Premendra Kumar (28/1/2010)</strong></li></ul><div><!--block--><strong>31-Jan-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->What can I do when my ownself is not with me rather this is against me</li><li><!--block--><strong>Premendra Kumar (31/1/2010)</strong></li><li><!--block-->I love you ****** But you never accepted me , your will !! I love you ******.</li></ul>','2018-05-25 15:19:12','2018-05-26 09:49:43',10,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
INSERT INTO `t_catg_ques_ans` VALUES (12,24,15,'<div><!--block--><strong>2009-2010</strong></div><ul><li><!--block-->In this copy I\'ll try to write down my wishes. I want to fulfill them. In&nbsp; stead of that I don\'t know whether I\'ll finally fulfill them or not. But they always pops in mind and I get inspired to fulfill them. What in future, I dont know, here I am mentioning them. -&nbsp;<strong>Premendra.</strong></li><li><!--block--><strong>7 Reasons to be happy</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Enjoy the present moment.</li><li><!--block-->To be happy now can benefit your future</li><li><!--block-->Turning into joy can improve your health.</li><li><!--block-->Feel you\'ll be always happy, you can do it right now.</li><li><!--block-->Everyday is a new opportunity to be better than yesterday.</li><li><!--block-->You can be who you want to be right now, no matter what your situation looks like.</li><li><!--block-->Finding joy in the present moment, this will make a difference.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>100 Reasons to be Happy today</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Every new day is another chance to change your life.</li><li><!--block-->This opportunity is an opportunity to be better than yesterday.</li><li><!--block-->You can be who you want to be right now.</li><li><!--block-->The glass is both half-empty and half-full.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Happiness comes from your own actions.</strong></li><li><!--block-->You have great friends.</li><li><!--block-->You can learn new thing today.</li><li><!--block-->The summer is coming soon.</li><li><!--block-->You are alive.</li><li><!--block-->You are already complete.</li><li><!--block-->You are unique.</li><li><!--block-->You have an influence on the world.</li><li><!--block-->You can change the world.</li><li><!--block-->You can feel emotions.</li><li><!--block-->You can change your perceptions.</li><li><!--block-->You have accomplished great things.</li><li><!--block-->You can be creative.</li><li><!--block-->You can change your state of mind by engaging in a physical activity.</li><li><!--block-->You can take responsibility and be empowered.</li><li><!--block--><strong>There is only now.</strong></li><li><!--block-->`Just think over what you do have and be happy.</li><li><!--block-->There is something good in everyday.</li><li><!--block-->You can eat something healthy today to make you feel good.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Life is beautiful.</strong></li><li><!--block-->We are in this life together.</li><li><!--block--><strong>Shared joy is a double joy, shared sorrow is half sorrow.</strong></li><li><!--block-->You can start writing down the good things that happen.</li><li><!--block-->You can achieve something today.</li><li><!--block-->The weather is good.</li><li><!--block-->You can listen to music.</li><li><!--block-->You can enjoy the sunrise.</li><li><!--block-->You can enjoy the sunset.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>What are primary responsibility of a Software Developer:-</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Primary responsibilities of a software developer is to&nbsp;<strong>analyse the problem and gather the information</strong>&nbsp;about a particular program, and then&nbsp;<strong>on the basis of the analysis the programmer makes an error-free program/software which meet all the requirement</strong>&nbsp;of the company.</li><li><!--block-->The developer is also responsible for making a program within due date. He should do proper documentation of the program so that it will be easier for a program so that it will be easier for a newcomer to easily understand the code and modify/change it according to required needs.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Different phases of software development.</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Requirement &amp; Analysis phase.</li><li><!--block-->Design phase</li><li><!--block-->Coding phase.</li><li><!--block-->Testing and Integration phase.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Software Developer responsibilities , in summary</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Time Bounded coding</li><li><!--block-->Proper Documentation for ease of understanding, modify or change according to requirement.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Top 10 qualities of Excellent Manager</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Creativity</li><li><!--block-->Structure</li><li><!--block-->Intuition</li><li><!--block-->Knowledge</li><li><!--block-->Commitment</li><li><!--block-->Being Human</li><li><!--block-->Versatility</li><li><!--block-->Lightness</li><li><!--block-->Discipline/Focus</li><li><!--block-->Big Picture, Small Actions.</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Top 10 Qualities of a Project Manager</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Inspires a shared vision</li><li><!--block-->Good Communicator</li><li><!--block-->Integrity</li><li><!--block-->Enthusiasm</li><li><!--block-->Empathy</li><li><!--block-->Competence</li><li><!--block-->Ability to delegate task</li><li><!--block-->Coolunder pressure</li><li><!--block-->Team building skills</li><li><!--block-->Problem solving skills</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Ten qualities of an Effective Team Player</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Demonstrate reliabilities</li><li><!--block-->Communicates constructively</li><li><!--block-->Listens actively</li><li><!--block-->Functions as an active paricipant</li><li><!--block-->Shares openly and willingly</li><li><!--block-->Cooperates and piches in to help.</li><li><!--block-->Exhibits flexibility</li><li><!--block-->Shows commitment to the team.</li><li><!--block-->Works as a problem-solver</li><li><!--block-->Treats others in a respectful and supportive manner</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Ten qualities of Valuable Employee</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Listening to instructions</li><li><!--block-->Taking responsibility</li><li><!--block-->Taking initiative</li><li><!--block-->Giving credit to others</li><li><!--block-->Being responsive</li><li><!--block-->Performing your duties cheerfully</li><li><!--block-->Being dependable</li><li><!--block-->Staying healthy</li><li><!--block-->Becoming self-displined</li><li><!--block-->Exceeding expectations</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Top 5 characteristics of the Ideal Employee</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Dependability</li><li><!--block-->Honesty &amp; Integrity</li><li><!--block-->Positive, proactive attitude</li><li><!--block-->Willing to work.</li><li><!--block-->Uses downtime productively</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>5 key qualities of a Good Employee</strong><ul><li><!--block-->Enthusiasm</li><li><!--block-->Strong work ethic</li><li><!--block-->Initiative</li><li><!--block-->Reliability</li><li><!--block-->Great communication skills</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>\"Kaam kahela ki humra chhu.. tab dekh.. Kaam Kaam ke sikhawela\"&nbsp; - Maa</strong></li><li><!--block--><strong>Duties &amp; Responsibilities of a Software Engineer</strong><ul><li><!--block-->A computer software engineer works in manufacturing, engineering, government and educational institutions. He uses his well-developed analytical and problem solving skills to design and develop sofware for business applications, computer game and operating systems</li></ul></li><li><!--block--><strong>Planning and Creating</strong><ul><li><!--block-->A software engineer begins each new task by analyzing the client\'s needs. He selects the mathematical, engineering and/or computer techniques that provides most efficient.</li></ul></li></ul>','2018-05-25 15:33:34','2018-05-25 17:36:37',10,'2018-08-16 16:13:02');
